            <abstract>
                <p>A collection of chants close to the Dǝggwā, but not identical to it. The colophon tells that the
                work was compiled by <persName ref="PRS11069Iyaqim">ʾabbā  Gera</persName> and <persName ref="PRS11069Iyaqim">ʾabbā
                Habla Śǝllāse</persName> from a number of Dǝggwā witnesses,
              following the order of <persName ref="PRS8550sardaDe">King Śarḍa Dǝngǝl</persName>.</p>
            </abstract>
